TextBody:
Hello all,

Thank you for your time in today's session.

In the meeting we have successfully fix the issue after we perform the following details. 

	granted the necessary permissions to the EPP client on the MacOS endpoint
	reinstall the EPP client due do to the missing IP, port and department which cause the issue, because the client was not communicating with the server
	add the EPP certificate to the MacOS machine. 
	check if the details are being populated in the local console and in the EPP UI

Since the issue is now solved we will proceed with the closure of this case.

Best regards,
